{
  "stem": "17.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that-- that narrowed down to-- to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what-- what you were fighting for.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After my mother left, we lived in the same house, yes, with my sister and us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we have to adjust somehow and go about our activities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I am trying to remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She-- she worked for the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were German industrialists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's was Schultz and Toebbens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were either sewing factories or other manufacturing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she worked for the-- for the Toebbens factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I know she had two friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were single girls, only left out of the whole families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they became close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I think they lived together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, later, they-- they moved, and they worked together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- and we again, were doing all different, like every day, different job, going to different workshop, and just living, spending one day after another.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we began to realize the reality of the situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People were coming back from concentration camps with the news.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At first, we didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We thought that they were crazy, that was maybe conspiracy to create a panic, to-- to-- to have people commit suicide or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the more and more news, and it sounded very real.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we began to think, what could be done?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That it cannot-- that-- that there is no future, and the persecution and the living conditions were completely-- they were impossible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very hard to-- to tolerate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] there were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not too many, not too much, that we could do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were already at the point of breaking, or breaking down.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
